abstract: >-
  bazi-life-curves is an open-source engine that translates traditional Chinese
  Bazi (Four Pillars of Destiny / 八字命理) analysis into deterministic, auditable,
  back-testable life curves across four dimensions (spirit / wealth / fame /
  relationship-energy) for up to 80 years. It cross-fuses three classical
  schools (Fu-Yi 扶抑 25%, Tiao-Hou 调候 40%, Ge-Ju 格局 30%) with Mang-Pai
  (盲派) event amplification, implements 10+ structural protection mechanisms
  (e.g. seal-protects-self, food-controls-killer, six-harmony-resolves-clash),
  enforces a three-stage handshake validation (R0+R1+R2) before output, and
  provides bit-for-bit deterministic results with a falsifiability protocol to
  prevent LLM hindsight rationalization. v7 adds LGBTQ+ / non-marital
  inclusivity by removing 600 years of feudal gender-discrimination rules
  (e.g. "wife harms husband" / "woman with strong food-god harms husband").
